  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "5 Sri Lankans who went to the Commonwealth tournament have Covid",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four players and a coach of the Sri Lankan team who left for the United Kingdom to join the Commonwealth tournament have tested positive for Covid. Two gymnasts, a gymnastics coach and a men's and women's basketball player are among those who have tested positive for Covid.",
        "These players and coaches have been given the opportunity to stay in an isolated hotel arranged by the Commonwealth Games organisers. They are recovering under medical supervision."
      ],
